name: Invite Only
description: Only users can join the chat room if they are invited to the room or are a room host or higher.

name: All Users
description: Any user can access this type of chat room.

name: Members Only
description: Guests are restricted from accessing a member only chat room.

name: Premium Only
description: Only user accounts who are premium or are a room host or higher may enter this room.

name: Moderators Only
description: Only user accounts who are a moderator or higher may enter this room.
